---
title: Spicy Veggie & Lentil Pilaf with Beetroot Slaw and Yoghurt
description: We love a good Pilaf  with Beetroot Slaw and Yoghurt and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-veggie-lentil-pilaf-e5f4b56e-28b7706a.jpg
